# resultType

**Instance Property**

The data type of the request’s result value.

## Declaration

```swift
var resultType: NSBatchDeleteRequestResultType { get }
```

## Discussion

This property’s value is set to the request’s [doc://com.apple.coredata/documentation/CoreData/NSBatchDeleteRequest/resultType] property.

## Accessing the Result

- **result**: The value the request returns after it executes.
- **NSBatchDeleteRequestResultType**: The types of result a batch delete request can provide when it executes.
